tissueExpression.summary: Membranous expression in a majority of tissues.
A majority of normal tissues displayed moderate to strong membranous staining. CNS and lymphoid tissues were negative.
Most cancer tissues displayed moderate to strong membranous positivity. Lymphomas, renal and hepatocellular carcinomas were negative.
